import Header from './Components/Header'
import MainPage from './Components/Mainpage'
export default function App(){
    return(
        <>
        <Header />
        <MainPage
            src="./images/Mount_Fuji.webp"
            country="japan"
            location='https://www.google.com/maps/@35.3625,138.7322,15z/data=!4m5!3m4!'
            date="12 Jan,2021 - 24 Jan,2021"
            detail="Mount Fuji, also known as Fuji-san, is the highest and most celebrated mountain in Japan, standing at 3,776 meters. It is arguably the most perfect volcano cone in existence, with a symmetrical shape that has inspired artists, poets, and pilgrims for centuries."
        />
        <MainPage />
        <MainPage />
        <MainPage />
        </>
    )
}
